    <item>
      <title>在美国关键通胀出现之前，金价攀升至新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/gold-retreats-as-robust-us-data-dampen-rate-cut-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者本周晚些时候将注意力转向关键的美国通胀数据，金价上涨至每盎司 2,350 美元上方的新纪录，而地缘政治风险也增加了金价的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/gold-retreats-as-robust-us-data-dampen-rate-cut-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 02:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
